original_title: Anvil Live At Wacken Open Air 1998
overview: Captured live at W:O:A Friday August 7 1998. Setlist: Five Knuckle Shuffle / Smoking Green / Old School / Winged Assassins / Forged in Fire / March of the Crabs / Metal on Metal / 666 / Mothra. Released as bonus disc with BACK TO BASICS.
